I play from time to time on Firiona. If you see a newbie beastlord clled
Ranii then send me a tell. I dont have equipment or gear to hand out but I
can share som knowledge about Norrath if theres anything you feel would help
you out.

Im normally a bit afk so might be a bit slow in answering but I dont mind
talking.
